node.text: Ok, it’s almost time for the wedding, which means it’s almost time for me to stop posting until after the episode airs bc all my remaining content contains SPOILERS 😬. But there was one more person I had to shout out on this season finale day, who brought so much to the show and whose departure leaves a big old hole... This was one of my favorite moments with @greg.germann, an actor whose *chef’s kiss* delivery made every joke 10x funnier and stole just about every scene he was in... Including this heartbreaking one. What an honor and pleasure to share the screen with you these past few years! xoxokm
